				<note xml:id="q-5b17e013-1390-e311-a968-000bdb5cc6d5" type="reporttext" n="31">Mail excised 293</note>
				<note xml:id="q-5c17e013-1390-e311-a968-000bdb5cc6d5" type="reporttext" n="32">NOTE: Low total of letters examined is due to small number of exam­iners now assigned to this office, which consists of a total officer per­sonnel of seven. Reduction in staff coincided with increase in amount of mail routed through this office, which accounts for the low percentage examined and inadequacy of checking.</note>
